milestones.description: Javed Miandad and Asif Mujtaba's 165-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 147 between Zaheer Abbas and Imran Khan
Wessels has broken the record for most catches (14) in ODIs for SA, going past McMillan's 13
This is the lowest match aggregate (376) involving teams South Africa & Pakistan in ODIs
Wessels has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (25) for SA, going past Richardson
